title: Number of operable nuclear reactor plants by country 2019
summary: This is a bar chart representing Country in the x axis and Number of reactors in the y axis.
Country United States has the highest Number of reactors and Iran has the lowest Number of reactors.
The minimum Country Iran has got 97.0 times less Number of reactors than the maximum Country United States.
